OL,3,CPrison officer jailed after sex with
OL,4,Cinmate and drug-smuggling plot
OL,6,FA former prison officer has been
OL,7,Fjailed for having illicit
OL,8,Frelationships with two inmates and
OL,9,Fplotting to smuggle drug-soaked
OL,10,Fenvelopes into jail.
OL,12,FIsabelle Dale, 23, became romantically
OL,13,Finvolved with prisoners Shahid Sharif
OL,14,Fand Connor Money and was "swearing
OL,15,Fthem undying love, saying she wanted
OL,16,Fto be with both of them on the
OL,17,Foutside", Judge Christopher Hehir said.
