OL,3,CPrison officer jailed after sex with
OL,4,Cinmate and drug-smuggling plot
OL,6,FShe got engaged to convicted robber
OL,7,FSharif, and later plotted with him and
OL,8,Fhis associate, Lilea Sallis, to
OL,9,Fsmuggle the synthetic cannabinoid,
OL,10,Fcommonly known as spice, into HMP
OL,11,FSwaleside on the Isle of Sheppey, Kent.
OL,13,FDale, of Cosham, Portsmouth, was
OL,14,Fsentenced to three and a half years'
OL,15,Fimprisonment for two counts of
OL,16,Fmisconduct in a public office between
OL,17,FSeptember 2021 and December 2022, and
OL,18,Fone count of conspiring to convey a
OL,19,FList A article into prison.
