OL,6,FSharif, who is already in custody at
OL,7,FHMP Wandsworth, and Sallis, were also
OL,8,Fjailed for the latter charge.
OL,10,FSentencing the three at Southwark
OL,11,FCrown Court on Tuesday, the judge told
OL,12,FDale: "I have concluded that
OL,13,Funfortunately you are a thoroughly
OL,14,Fdevious and untruthful and
OL,15,Fmanipulative young woman.
