OL,3,CPrison officer jailed after sex with
OL,4,Cinmate and drug-smuggling plot
OL,6,F"I accept you have some
OL,7,Fvulnerabilities but, as was apparent
OL,8,Fin your evidence, you seek to use them
OL,9,Fas a shield and an excuse for your
OL,10,Factions. But they did not provide
OL,11,Fthat."
OL,13,FHe added: "I suspect you actually
OL,14,Fjoined the prison service with a view
OL,15,Fto becoming involved in criminal
OL,16,Factivities with prisoners."
OL,18,FDale arrived at HMP Coldingley,
OL,19,FSurrey, in September 2021 for what
OL,20,Fwould be her first and only posting.
