OL,6,FBy January, she and Sharif had had "at
OL,7,Fleast some contact" because she
OL,8,Fmentioned him to a senior colleague `
OL,9,Fby May they were engaged, the court
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FThe trial was told the prison officer,
OL,13,Fwho has since resigned, had sex with
OL,14,FSharif in the chapel area of HMP
OL,15,FColdingley.
