OL,4,Cinmate and drug-smuggling plot
OL,6,FJudge Hehir said he could not know if
OL,7,Fthey were intimate in the chapel area
OL,8,Fbut text messages show they "clearly
OL,9,Fhad a sexual relationship" and other
OL,10,Fprison officers "obviously had clocked
OL,11,Fon to what was going on".
OL,13,FSharif was at the time serving a 12-
OL,14,Fyear and 10-month sentence for an
OL,15,F"extremely violent robbery of a
OL,16,Fjewellers on the south coast", the
OL,17,Fjudge added.
OL,19,FDale's home was searched and a "rather
OL,20,Fgarish" picture of the couple was
OL,21,Ffound hanging above her bed, he said.
