OL,6,FIt had photographs of them "spliced
OL,7,Ftogether" with a white heart between
OL,8,Fand the date May 17 2022, believed to
OL,9,Fbe the day of their engagement.
OL,11,FAfter the chapel incident, Sharif
OL,12,Fmoved to Swaleside prison and Dale
OL,13,Fsigned off work sick on reduced pay.
OL,15,FTheir relationship continued and Dale
OL,16,Fwas involved in the drug smuggling
OL,17,Fconspiracy while still employed as
OL,18,Fprison officer, the court heard.
