OL,6,FIn a demonstration of "quite how
OL,7,Fthoroughly corrupt you had become",
OL,8,FDale attempted to persuade Sharif's
OL,9,Fsister to sneak in a USB for him, he
OL,10,Ftold the court, which the sibling
OL,11,Fdeclined to do.
OL,13,FThe prison officer also passed
OL,14,Fmessages to Sharif's criminal
OL,15,Fassociates outside the jail "about the
OL,16,Fmovement or sale of what I'm quite
OL,17,Fsure was illicit property", the judge
OL,18,Fsaid.
