OL,6,FShe also posted stories and used the
OL,7,Fmessaging service on his social media
OL,8,Faccount on his behalf.
OL,10,FDale resigned as a prison officer
OL,11,Fbefore she was arrested on her sixth
OL,12,Fvisit.
OL,14,FShe was found to have Sharif's street
OL,15,Fname tattooed on her neck as well as
OL,16,Fan engagement ring and carbon paper in
OL,17,Fher car, the court heard.
OL,19,FCarbon paper can be used to disguise
OL,20,Fcontraband from x-rays.
