OL,6,FThe judge said evidence put to the
OL,7,Fjury showed she "well understood what
OL,8,Fcorruption was and the risks and
OL,9,Fdangers relating to it".
OL,11,FHe added: "She wanted to do it. I
OL,12,Fthink she's attention seeking and I
OL,13,Fthink she seeks validation and I think
OL,14,Fshe did that through relationships
OL,15,Fwith prisoners."
