OL,6,F"I don't think she had a fit of
OL,7,Fconscience, to put it that way, but I
OL,8,Fthink that's why her enthusiasm
OL,9,Fcooled," he added.
OL,11,FSharif attended proceedings via video
OL,12,Flink from prison.
OL,14,FHe previously admitted conspiring to
OL,15,Fbring the drug into Swaleside and the
OL,16,Ftwo women, who had denied the charge,
OL,17,Fwere convicted by a jury.
OL,19,FSallis was sentenced to two and a half
OL,20,Fyears in jail and Sharif received 27
OL,21,Fmonths.
